
You can download nifticlib from here:
http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/niftilib/nifticlib/nifticlib_2_0_0/nifticlib-2.0.0.tar.gz

build:
 - uncompress and expand to make nifticlib-2.0.0 directory
 - cd into directory
 - type "make"

use "make clean_all" to undo the make. (the form it is in repository)
